866
00:36:50,300 --> 00:36:52,260
Yes, selling leather shoes.

867
00:36:52,340 --> 00:36:54,500
Purchase, sale, keeping accounts.

868
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:55,940
All me.

869
00:36:56,900 --> 00:36:57,980
Do you know how to make report forms?

870
00:36:58,580 --> 00:37:00,460
Of course.

871
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:03,660
